Art From The Heart is a service based club that brings students together to create crafts for various organizations, spreading cheer through creativity.

Projects we might be doing throughout the year include: bracelet making for HALO, paper crane folding for Cranes for Cancer, paper flower making at a senior center, Little Green Monster sewing projects, testing divider painting, and so much more!
